          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Just as a side note to our younger readers, whom other automotive sites have to treat as total idiots who know nothing about cars: the Amazon has nothing to do with the retail site you undoubtedly know and love. It was actually a small, pretty gutless little Swedish car most people didn’t pay attention to. This is what makes it perfect fodder for the Chip Foose Draws A Car video series since most people won’t have an opinion on it either way.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
