        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "A growing number of tuners have been using the Amazon for their mad scientist projects. Some of these guys have done ",
